snippet.title: Crab Raid Tactics Steam Demo Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the Raid Leader for a squad of greedy crustaceans! Crab Raid Tactics is a Real-Time Combat Strategy with Roguelike elements, where each battle requires your quick strategic reaction to the changes on the battlefield.

Wishlist & try the demo  on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2374290/Crab_Raid_Tactics/

https://twitter.com/CrabRaidTactics
A game by Stefan Sadchikov https://twitter.com/srvelat
Crab Art by Derek Souza  https://twitter.com/derekpxart

Music:
https://pixabay.com/music/soft-house-tropical-house-121742/
